<p>Nakiisa si City Mayor Marilou Flores-Morillo sa isinagawang  “Partnership of Philippine Support Service Agencies, Inc. (PHILSSA) Board Meeting”, kasama si Ms. Doris G. Melgar (President, People’s Council of Calapan City) at CAO Supervising Head, Mr. Avelino P. Tejada, ginanap sa ABC Hall, DILG Building, City Hall, nitong ika-8 ng Abril. Ang PHILSSA ay isang national network ng social development organizations na pangunahing umaaksyon at nangangasiwa sa mga urban issue at concern.</p><p><br></p><p><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," style="width: 25%;"><br></p>
